                    <span>I have never been to Tuscany nor even Italy, but after this book, I can hardly wait to go. If the author and photographer were able to stay in all the places mentioned, they were truly lucky. I have lent this book to friends who HAVE been to Tuscany, and mostly they are sorry they missed so many of the beautiful homes etc. But, universally, they say that it gives them a good excuse to go back for another visit! Well done to both author and photographer!</span>
                  
              
